Bufo Keyboard
=============

This application bundles bufo emoji assets sourced from the bufo.fun project:
  https://github.com/tfritzy/bufo.fun

Per the bufo.fun project README, the bufo collection is distributed under the
MIT License. The bufo.fun collection is itself derived from the all-the-bufo
collection at https://github.com/knobiknows/all-the-bufo, which is the
upstream source of many of the individual sprites. Individual bufo sprites
have been contributed by many people across the community; please see the
bufo.fun project for attribution of individual works.

The bufo.fun project's stated license terms (MIT) are reproduced below.

